    "client_msg_id": "7e36f11c-11af-4d29-b26e-df6da1dade76",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Nice. It'll be interesting to see how these LLM code modification tools scale beyond trivial use cases. What are your thoughts currently on the plausibility and challenges of using something like Magnet for codebases way beyond 10 000 LOCs?",
